law.text: Each application for a license as a master or journeyman plumber shall be accompanied by a reasonable fee as established by the department.
law.history: Amended 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 24, sec. 1674, effective July 15, 2010. -- Amended 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 193, sec. 2. -- Amended 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 222, sec. 6, effective June 16, 1960. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 3909b-1.
